'''''Medora''''' is a genus of [[gastropods]] belonging to the family [[Clausiliidae]].<ref name="GBIF">{{cite web |title=Medora H.Adams & A.Adams, 1855 |url=https://www.gbif.org/species/3243940 |website=www.gbif.org |access-date=1 November 2021 |language=en}}</ref>

The species of this genus are found in South Europe and [[Mediterranean]].<ref name="GBIF" />

Species:<ref name="GBIF" />

*''[[Medora adensameri]]'' {{small|H.Nordsieck, 2009}}
*''[[Medora agnata]]'' {{small|(L.Pfeiffer, 1842)}}
*''[[Medora almissana]]'' {{small|(Küster, 1847)}}
*''[[Medora armata]]'' {{small|(Küster, 1844)}}
*''[[Medora contracta]]'' {{small|(Rossmässler, 1842)}}
*''[[Medora dalmatina]]'' {{small|(Rossmässler, 1835)}}
*''[[Medora eris]]'' {{small|(L.Pfeiffer, 1866)}}
*''[[Medora garganensis]]'' {{small|(A.J.Wagner, 1918)}}
*''[[Medora hiltrudae]]'' {{small|H.Nordsieck, 1970}}
*''[[Medora italiana]]'' {{small|(Küster, 1847)}}
*''[[Medora lesinensis]]'' {{small|(Küster, 1847)}}
*''[[Medora macascarensis]]'' {{small|(G.B.Sowerby I, 1828)}}
*''[[Medora milettiana]]'' {{small|Giusti, 1967}}
*''[[Medora pollinensis]]'' {{small|H.Nordsieck, 2012}}
*''[[Medora proxima]]'' {{small|(Walderdorff, 1864)}}
*''[[Medora punctulata]]'' {{small|(Küster, 1850)}}
*''[[Medora stenostoma]]'' {{small|(Rossmässler, 1839)}}

